{
  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view showcases a vibrant city skyline illuminated by numerous lights, with a bridge prominently featured in the foreground. Fireworks explode above one of the tallest skyscrapers, creating a spectacular display of red, white, and blue bursts. The bridge, seemingly a modern suspension or cable-stayed structure, is lit with a continuous row of white lights, guiding the eye across a dark body of water. Behind it, a more traditional bridge with classic support pillars is partially visible.  The cityscape is densely packed with buildings of varying heights, all glowing with a multitude of colors. The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and urban grandeur.",
